# HenoBack Office — Marketing Website

## Product

HenoBack Office: outsourced accounting, controller support, and finance operations for **professional service firms**. Part of the Heno platform; advisory parent is IFI Professionals.

## Canonical references

- Production (content source of truth): https://henobackoffice.com
- Design reference (layout / typography): https://ifi-website.vercel.app
- Logo: `public/henoback-office-logo.png` (add asset; do not use emoji placeholders)
- Brand accent: `#F27830` (Heno orange)

## Stack

Next.js 14 App Router, Tailwind, static marketing pages. Standalone site — **not** the GTM admin app.

## Migration strategy

**B → A (default):** Ship on Vercel project `henoback-website` (preview URL) until stakeholder sign-off, then point `henobackoffice.com` DNS to Vercel. Do not use hybrid “new home + legacy deep links” unless explicitly requested.

## Design principles

- White backgrounds, generous whitespace, real logo
- Inter or system sans; neutral-900 text, neutral-100 borders
- Subtle glass surfaces (`backdrop-blur`, white/70 panels) — 2027 designer feel, not heavy chrome
- Rounded-full primary CTAs; minimal chrome like IFI site
- Mobile-first; sticky header with logo + phone + Book a consultation

## Brand strings (use consistently)

| Context | String |
|--------|--------|
| Product / nav / CTAs | **HenoBack Office** |
| Legal footer | **Heno BackOffice Services** |
| Parent | **IFI Professionals** · Heno platform |
| Avoid without rebrand decision | “HENO BackOffice Solutions” (live WordPress header) |

## CTAs & routing

- Primary: **Book a consultation** → GTM intake with UTMs (`utm_source=henoback-www`, `utm_campaign=henoback_office`)
- Secondary: **Take the assessment** → `journeys/outsource` on GTM app
- Use `NEXT_PUBLIC_GTM_APP_URL` for cross-app links (no hardcoded production URLs in components)

## GTM attribution (separate apps)

- This site = marketing + SEO + trust. GTM engine = forms, journeys, lead tracking.
- All GTM outbound links go through `lib/gtm-links.ts` with `utm_source=henoback-www`, `utm_campaign=henoback_office`, and `utm_content` per page/CTA.
- Campaigns use **this site’s URLs** in ads/email; CTAs hand off to GTM with consistent UTMs. See `docs/GTM-ATTRIBUTION.md`.

## Content rules

- **Word-for-word** copy from henobackoffice.com unless marketing approves a change. Store in `lib/content/*.ts`.
- Elevate presentation (2027 glass UI) — do not paraphrase body copy during migration
- Services (9): Bookkeeping, Full Service Accounting, Payroll Integration, Audit Support, Budgeting & Forecasting, Accounting Analysis, CFO Outsourcing, AP/AR, Expense Automation
- Industries (9): Management Consulting, Project Accounting, Creative Agencies, Technology & IT, HR & Talent, Engineering/Architecture/Environmental, Government Contracting, Real Estate, Specialized Advisory
- Contact: (702) 729-6682, info@HenoBackOffice.com
- Jim French founder block: one strong section, used sparingly

## Vercel

- Project: `henoback-website`
- Env: `NEXT_PUBLIC_GTM_APP_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL`

## Do not

- Add GTM admin, Supabase, or campaign logic to this site
- Shrink the offer (no “3 service cards” stubs)
- Commit `.env` or secrets
- Mix this UI context with GTM admin slate UI in the same prompt
